现在，我们的第一步是配制Fe₂(SO₄)₃溶液并测定其初始pH值。你可以用滴管将8 mL的Fe₂(SO₄)₃溶液加入试管，然后插入pH计测量。这样我们就能为后续实验打下基础。你觉得可以从这里开始吗？如果有任何不确定的地方，我可以随时帮你解答！",1.646090534979424,1.2396694214876034,1.646090534979424,3.0136351121383926,9,"The tutor effectively used the PREDICTIVE_QUESTIONING strategy to guide the student toward understanding the risk of heating glassware to 500°C. By asking thought-provoking questions about the physical limits of glass and providing relevant data, the tutor encouraged the student to critically evaluate their assumption. Additionally, the tutor redirected the student to the correct experimental procedure, ensuring safety and focus on the task. This approach demonstrated strong pedagogical skill and Socratic teaching principles.",9,64
